{"tid":443492,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"其實是咪得香港人會改洋名","createTime":"2017-10-21T15:18:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-21T19:15:39.000Z","uid":75209,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"93aa02d6ba8c773043630e3a55759369149a953c","tid":443492,"uid":75209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T15:18:58.000Z","msg":"其他非英語國家嘅人，好少會好似香港人咁改Mary, Tom, John, Peter 果啲洋名，多數會用返本名，好似日本人叫Yuki... 印度人叫Singh, 好少聽日本人叫自己做John, Mary... <br />\n<br />\n其實點解唔可以用返自己本名，呀明就叫Ming, 健仔就呀Kin, 其實有乜問題？<br />\n<br />\n(已經唔係講緊咩Apple, Zero, Cherry, Queenie.. 果啲怪名)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe02e83efdd44ca2e77e4c1348756a32b40e968d","tid":443492,"uid":71568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T15:24:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58b65ad3eb8b2a7b26383e52dfe491d853afc80e","tid":443492,"uid":33643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T15:32:32.000Z","msg":"漢字影響區黎講，韓 中 台都common<br />\n尤其是要返工對鬼佬個班<br />\n<br />\n但日真係少"},{"pid":"843127442792e4d0c51849da33b6186860663b15","tid":443492,"uid":74497,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T15:33:42.000Z","msg":"諗起有個台灣節目<br />\nD鬼佬問點解你地要特登去改個英文名"},{"pid":"81d66341702dfd15907f26750aa579cd44276ee2","tid":443492,"uid":101726,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T15:42:36.000Z","msg":"因為宗教原因都會改嘅<br />\n傳統基督徒受洗會有個christian name<br />\n伊斯蘭教徒好似都會改返個阿拉伯名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4ff92db7b6982de6882cf3ddddf05724dd68649","tid":443492,"uid":27210,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T15:45:06.000Z","msg":"樓主知唔知香港做咗英國殖民地100年"},{"pid":"ca2e4f945a6a90ff11e1c52d4b9755709d21b98f","tid":443492,"uid":33643,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T16:06:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諗起有個台灣節目<br />\nD鬼佬問點解你地要特登去改個英文名</blockquote><br />\n方便佢地叫，廢事叫錯"},{"pid":"bc036145aff9a5ba4d9b3fb573da62c894a6b386","tid":443492,"uid":5150,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T17:08:01.000Z","msg":"係因為啲教畜會話啊Sing啊Wing啊King唔係英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba92232b53a160bf0cdf974746a130c612f8883e","tid":443492,"uid":72608,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T17:09:16.000Z","msg":"因為由小學中學開始英文堂老師就幫你改定1個洋英文名"},{"pid":"22b5522a836b180ff82d53c2012bfa62f468fd6a","tid":443492,"uid":68641,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T17:10:04.000Z","msg":"激烈的海膽"},{"pid":"5207cb8707df69078d94a9dc199669ab7ad063d0","tid":443492,"uid":13187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T17:17:43.000Z","msg":"MoonMoon"},{"pid":"d7fb2edff0f95312427c60cbd57f9fa7bdb1b481","tid":443492,"uid":75209,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T18:30:37.000Z","msg":"所以就係唔明點解學校，尤其係local 果渣<br />\n一定要學生改洋名，英文科老師又唔見得自己英文有幾好，書唔識教反而著重埋哩啲柒嘢，真係諗唔明<br />\n<br />\n反而真係講英文嘅國際學校，先唔會逼學生改名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n樓上有巴打話關港英時代事，但印度，部分中東國家，都比英國管治過，唔見得果啲人係咁"},{"pid":"696436e393ce400d2df7d2224d4dc25dc346f062","tid":443492,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T18:32:40.000Z","msg":"其實樓主有冇讀歷史"},{"pid":"c2d0af53f604e81c06449564caa829d9cdd1a876","tid":443492,"uid":65660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T18:33:40.000Z","msg":"咁我想問有英文名又有乜問題？<br />\n我好肯定樓主你自己都有"},{"pid":"8e76105891c060a9dfd3f86a5c988cc966a4e2f3","tid":443492,"uid":15010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T18:39:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主知唔知香港做咗英國殖民地100年</blockquote><br />\n佢岀世個陣已經唔係<br />\n樓主做完功課未？"},{"pid":"48e97bc82169b7e44e891475ca555bd3240ed50a","tid":443492,"uid":10023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T18:42:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其他非英語國家嘅人，好少會好似香港人咁改Mary, Tom, John, Peter 果啲洋名，多數會用返本名，好似日本人叫Yuki... 印度人叫Singh, 好少聽日本人叫自己做John, Mary... <br />\n<br />\n其實點解唔可以用返自己本名，呀明就叫Ming, 健仔就呀Kin, 其實有乜問題？<br />\n<br />\n(已經唔係講緊咩Apple, Zero, Cherry, Queenie.. 果啲怪名)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n印度個個都singh<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dab9fc9f2b82620f2e314df59c384361991b2bc0","tid":443492,"uid":13616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T18:58:22.000Z","msg":"我覺得因為廣東人有d姓同名好難發音<br />\n姓tse 姓ng咁<br />\n同埋又太小姓氏好易撞<br />\n所以有必要改英文名"},{"pid":"4266f2f136c34a1f30a48b366203c25e1eeccb10","tid":443492,"uid":154708,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T19:15:39.000Z","msg":"如果用最後一個字介紹自己<br />\n咁嗰啲叫咩咩豪或者咩咩浩嘅人係咪要自介話<br />\n&quot;Hi I am ho (hoe)&quot;<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/22/031408_5731959a6d2bffc2814baf096bda985f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F22%2F031408_5731959a6d2bffc2814baf096bda985f.jpg&h=4551a9dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n情況大概係咁...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：用開小學雞英文名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}